TASK_DESCRIPTION=The intent fallback Opus should proactively use tools/commands to answer questions instead of giving static responses. When user asks about projects, it should run find/ls, check doey list, scan for package.json/go.mod/Cargo.toml etc. Requirements: (1) Remove --no-tools from fallback Opus calls so it can use tools. (2) Increase max-turns enough for useful multi-step work. (3) Enrich system prompt to encourage proactive tool use and filesystem exploration. (4) It should know about doey projects via doey list command.
